title: Nasty Nancy (2010 - Croatia) school girl splatter gore horror
description:
Nasty Nancy (2010 - Croatia)

Splatter / Gore / Horror

written and directed by Sandi Mance

no IMDb listing but youtube has official trailer


Castrum Films Production

In a school full of perverse teachers, where you earn grades by having sex, Nancy is the only honest person. But when she, despite studying a lot, fails her final exam it's time for revenge!

No, it's not a porn flick as the summary strongly suggests. It's an amateur Croatian splatter short movie, which impressively has Miroslav Lakobrija, the special effects supervisor for A Serbian Film doing the effects here as well.


Video: XviD, 704x400, 25.000 fps, 1210 Kbps, 00h48m50s
Audio: MP3, 48000 Hz, joint stereo, 128 kbps

DVDRip, Croatian audio, English subtitles hardcoded
